text:
Willow Smith felt as if she lost her "sanity" after having had success in the music industry at the age of nine.

In the second episode of her mother Jada Pinkett Smith's 's Facebook Watch series Red Table Talk Willow released her hit "Whip My Hair" in 2010. During the episode that focused on the loss, Jada Willow asked what her biggest loss to date was her life.

"I really feel like I've lost my mind at some point," Willow confessed. "It was after all the Whip My Hair thing and I had just stopped giving voice lessons and I was kind of in that gray area of" Who am I? "Do I have a purpose? anything else I can do? ""? "
title: Jada Pinkett Smith Tears Up Learning's daughter Willow used to cut herself – NewsBeezer
